snippet.title: Dark Souls II: Crown of the Ivory King - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Crown of the Ivory King, the third expansion pack, is now available for Dark Souls II.

Follow Dark Souls II at GameSpot.com!
http://www.gamespot.com/dark-souls-ii/

Check out our review!
